long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This year UI Gudetama theme offers ever more custom and cool features. Some of these include custom gudetama wallpapers, Quick links, Student Links, Developer Searching and more ! 

Latest updates - 08/03/2023

Version 5.00 supports both MacOS and Windows all almost all devices

Newest update Includes:

- Bug issues fixed
- New design to wallpaper
- New Extension Logo and wallpaper design (Season Matching)
- Light & Dark mode support on all devices
- Student Tool - edu and gov sites ( Day Map, One school, OneDrive )
